      <title>油价接近三个月低点，欧佩克+供应增加，美国需求成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油价格在经历了四年来的最大单周跌幅后企稳，市场关注焦点是周日举行的欧佩克+供应会议以及夏季驾车季节开始时的美国需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 23:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市上涨，美元下跌，因美联储放宽政策的希望：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/asian-stocks-to-climb-as-risk-sentiment-rebounds-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于押注美联储今年将降息，亚洲股市上涨，而美元走软，本周公布的美国通胀数据可能预示物价压力有所缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/asian-stocks-to-climb-as-risk-sentiment-rebounds-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 22:57:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>潜在买家找到，恒大电动车股价飙升113%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/evergrande-ev-unit-says-its-liquidators-found-a-potential-buyer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的房地产开发商中国恒大集团的电动汽车部门股价上涨了一倍多，此前该公司表示，清算人正在与潜在买家就入股该公司进行谈判，并可能提供新的信贷额度以支持生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/evergrande-ev-unit-says-its-liquidators-found-a-potential-buyer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 12:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
